*Vikenda* je vreme za odmor i opuštanje. (Weekend is a time for relaxation and rest.)

Radim puno tokom radnog vikenda. (I work a lot during the workweek.)

Većina ljudi voli da se opusti tokom vikenda. (Most people like to relax during the weekend.)

Želim da provedem vikend sa prijateljima. (I want to spend the weekend with friends.)

Vikend je idealan za odlazak na putovanje. (The weekend is ideal for a trip.)